postReview.title: Brighton 2-1 Newcastle United: El ex 'Black Cat' Welbeck continúa acosando a Howe

postReview.title: Brighton 2-1 Newcastle United: Ex-Black Cat Welbeck continues to haunt Howe
postReview.description: Danny Welbeck scored either side of Nick Woltemade's backheel as Brighton defeated Newcastle United 2-1 in the Premier League.
